stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OpenChatbot
    OpenChatbot --> TypeMessage
    TypeMessage --> SendMessage : POST /api/chatbot/send/
    SendMessage --> ClassifyIntent
    ClassifyIntent --> HandleGreeting : Greeting detected
    ClassifyIntent --> HandleSecurityQ : Security question
    ClassifyIntent --> FallbackResponse : Unknown intent
    HandleGreeting --> DisplayResponse
    HandleSecurityQ --> RuleBasedLookup
    RuleBasedLookup --> DisplayResponse
    FallbackResponse --> DisplayResponse
    DisplayResponse --> TypeMessage : Continue chat
    DisplayResponse --> [*]